Package io.github.eutro.jwasm

Class ModuleVisitor

java.lang.Object
io.github.eutro.jwasm.BaseVisitor<ModuleVisitor>
io.github.eutro.jwasm.ModuleVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
ModuleNode, ModuleWriter
public class ModuleVisitor extends BaseVisitor<ModuleVisitor>
A visitor that visits a WebAssembly module.

The structure and order of visits fits the binary format rather than the common syntax format.

Methods are expected to be called in the order:

visitHeader ( visitCustom )* [ visitTypes ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitImports ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitFuncs ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitTables ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitMems ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitGlobals ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitExports ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitStart ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitElems ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitDataCount ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitCode ] ( visitCustom )* [ visitDatas ] ( visitCustom )* visitEnd
